CAST(SYS_EXTRACT_UTC(CAST(''01-JAN-70'' AS TIMESTAMP(6))) AS DATE)) * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000) AS INTEGER) as ' || c.column_name ||',' WHEN c.data_type = 'BLOB' THEN 'utl_raw.cast_to_varchar2(dbms_lob.substr('|| c.column_name ||')) as ' || c.column_name ||',' WHEN c.data_type = 'RAW' THEN 'convert('|| c.column_name ||',''WE8ISO8859P1'') as ' || c.column_name ||',' WHEN c.data_type like '%CLOB' THEN 'replace(replace('|| c.column_name ||',chr(13),''''),chr(34),chr(34)||chr(34)) as ' || c.column_name ||',' WHEN c.data_type like '%CHAR%' THEN 'replace(replace('|| c.column_name ||',chr(13),''''),chr(34),chr(34)||chr(34)) as ' || c.column_name ||',' WHEN c.data_type like '%FLOAT%' THEN 'CAST('|| c.column_name ||' as NUMBER(38,9)) as ' || c.column_name ||',' ELSE c.column_name || ',' END).EXTRACT('//text()') ORDER BY c.column_id).GetClobVal(),','),''||chr(38)||'apos;','''') from all_tab_cols c where table_name = '${table_name:substringAfter('.')}' and owner = '${table_name:substringBefore('.')}' and HIDDEN_COLUMN = 'NO' and column_id is not null and ${columns_where_clause}) column_list FROM all_views b WHERE b.owner = '${table_name:substringBefore('.')}' AND b.view_name='${table_name:substringAfter('.')}'

update JUNIPER_EXT_NIFI_STATUS set status='FAILED', COMMENTS = CONCAT(COMMENTS,'Column metadata fetch failed for table/view ${table_name:substringAfter('.')};') where feed_unique_name='${feed_name}' and run_id='${run_id}' and job_type='R'

select incr_value as pre_max_value from JUNIPER_EXT_TABLE_STATUS where table_name='${table_name}' and FEED_UNIQUE_NAME='${feed_name}' and WHERE_CLAUSE='${where_clause:replace("'","''")}' and RUN_ID = (select max(RUN_ID) from juniper_ext_nifi_status where FEED_UNIQUE_NAME='${feed_name}' and status = 'SUCCESS' and job_type='R')
